<refnamediv><refname>dnn_nms</refname><refpurpose>Apply non-maximum suppression to bounding boxes.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>keep = dnn_nms(boxes, scores, scoreThreshold, nmsThreshold)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>dnn_nms</function> returns the indices of boxes kept after IoU-based suppression.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
boxes = [0 0 10 10; 1 1 10 10; 50 50 10 10];
keep = dnn_nms(boxes, [0.9; 0.8; 0.7], 0.1, 0.5);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
